            "description": "Sync has been suspended for lock `{lock_entity_id}`.\n\n**Reason:** {reason}\n\nThe lock will resume syncing automatically when it recovers. Click **Submit** to acknowledge this issue."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "lock_offline": {
      "title": "Lock unreachable: {lock_entity_id}",
      "description": "Lock Code Manager has been unable to communicate with `{lock_entity_id}` for multiple consecutive attempts. Code synchronization is paused until the lock is reachable again. This issue will be automatically dismissed when the lock recovers."
    }
  }
}

